weave.utils

Class SQLResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • weave.utils.SQLResult

  • public class SQLResult
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a lightweight object that holds the data in a 2D Array from a ResultSet. The column names and their corresponding type are stored in an array (columnNames and columnTypes respectively)
    Author:
    Andy Dufilie
